{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2128178, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "通货膨胀", "timestamp": 1627141122, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2128183, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "通货膨胀", "timestamp": 1627141165, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2128185, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果你有房，再随便搞点投资，这样确实可以", "timestamp": 1627141196, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2128187, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": 2128183, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 应该肯定不会闲着，每月搞个轻松的副业呗", "timestamp": 1627141204, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2128191, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": 2128185, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 没房只有三百万不行吗", "timestamp": 1627141228, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2128224, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": 2128191, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 通胀肯定比银行利率高得多，还得考虑父母生病，自己养老。个人感觉至少得有个房子，当然我也不是专业的，就随便说说。", "timestamp": 1627141506, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2128362, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "家里确实有三四百现金hh", "timestamp": 1627142471, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2128388, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "害怕突发情况导致300w没了，比如家人生大病", "timestamp": 1627142745, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2129349, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": 2128191, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 不行，等你有三百万你就会意识到财富是资产，不是货币，在此基础上不难判断出即使房租比等值货币的利息少，也应该把货币转化为房产", "timestamp": 1627156128, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2129376, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": 2129349, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 有百分之四的回报的货币就已经是资产了。", "timestamp": 1627167732, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2129674, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": 2129349, "tag": null, "text": "Re Francis: 中国大部分地区的房产根本就不是资产，充其量只是过去十年二十年搭上了核心资产涨价的便车而已。", "timestamp": 1627177550, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130854, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": 2129674, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 非北上广深的房子没啥金融价值吧", "timestamp": 1627192971, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2130872, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 412928, "reply_to": 2129376, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 货币是否是资产取决于拥有货币的人能否把货币转化为资产，对于金融机构来说货币当然是资产，但对于大多数普通人来说货币只不过就是用来消费的数字。你说的百分之四回报率真的不高，一千万现金随便找个银行都能轻轻松松地稳赚10%以上不赔，但远远比不上一线（防杠）房产保值，房产是货币铆钉点，而你把钱给银行只是银行赚钱分你点油水而已", "timestamp": 1627193435, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 412928, "reply": 13, "tag": null, "text": "我突然意识到，按照利率0.04，只要手上有三百万，那么每年的利率最少12万，每月一万生活费（房租+吃饭购物即使在一线肯定也够，不要孩子不结婚，嫌弃生活不好还可以去南方二三线更爽），是不是就可以不用工作享受人生了？\n所以是，赚到300万，就可以退休啦？", "timestamp": 1627141104, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1627193435, "url": "", "vote": {}}}